## Additional Terms for HealthTrace Platform

### Data Usage and Privacy
- This software is designed to handle health and environmental data in compliance with GDPR and Italian data protection laws
- Users must ensure proper anonymization of patient data before processing
- Environmental data should be sourced from authorized Italian agencies (ARPA, ISPRA, ISTAT)

### Academic and Research Use
- Academic institutions may use this software for non-commercial research purposes
- Commercial use requires proper licensing and compliance with Italian health regulations
- Publications using this software should cite the HealthTrace project appropriately

### Italian Health Authority Compliance
- This software is designed to comply with Italian Ministry of Health guidelines
- Users are responsible for ensuring compliance with local health regulations
- Integration with official health surveillance systems requires proper authorization

For commercial licensing or integration with official health systems, contact: licensing@healthtrace.it